{"tid":1262954,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"神燈燒山","createTime":"2019-06-28T02:46:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-28T07:27:54.000Z","uid":28534,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"5c33e14f0203169c39c73162beb2cce4f8efb635","tid":1262954,"uid":28534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T02:46:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190628&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=59765807\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190628%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D59765807&d=CAukz3ZnfWt5Iztj8dmWPFe0bVP%2BLlUkdLfYKyPPBhg%3D&h=8a3a0cee\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190628%26s%3D6996647%26a%3D59765807&h=4c20b138\" target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190628&amp;s=6996647&amp;a=59765807</a><br />\n<br />\n林鄭昨日會見一批政商界代表。報道指出，林鄭在開場白中表明，中央對自己仍十分支持，她不想為中央增添麻煩，所以她一定不會辭職；第二，在現時的環境下，一定要支持警方，這點尤其重要。第三，不會成立獨立調查委員會，調查警方對反修例示威者使用武力的情況，因此做法只會針對警方，認為一個公平做法，第四，她認為若答應不起訴6.12警民衝突的示威者，認為這做法等如干預司法。<br />\n<br />\n報道指出，林鄭在會上稱中央曾派出中間人向她了解狀態，她笑言：「好多人以為我死了，但我不會死得去。」<br />\n<br />\n燒山好野"},{"pid":"b9a0160f0185f07c3b5498f9e34f09ef0bce5857","tid":1262954,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T02:49:45.000Z","msg":"真係好燈<br />\n燒山唔該毒啞自己啦"},{"pid":"02d6dde5a839151fa91f39e2f38698b202d91d12","tid":1262954,"uid":160537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T02:59:29.000Z","msg":"又燈。。<br />\n屌佢老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2536a1c3206e35fb2a66385189065e30ba7bf2af","tid":1262954,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-28T03:00:04.000Z","msg":"第三<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64966299c789cc7d3117c908391629ce0c543e69","tid":1262954,"uid":143572,"like":1,"dislike":1